videos.headline: Hason Ward comes up with the big block for Iowa State
videos.description: Hason Ward gets up high on the glass to deny Baylor a bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hason Ward comes up with the big block for Iowa State) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tamin Lipsey gets the steal and turns it into 2
videos.description: Tamin Lipsey capitalizes on Baylor's mistake and finds Jaren Holmes for an easy bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Tamin Lipsey gets the steal and turns it into 2) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Bridges makes the and-1 for Baylor
videos.description: Jalen Bridges muscles his way in for a tough layup and gets the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Bridges makes the and-1 for Baylor) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Adam Flagler beats the halftime buzzer with logo 3-pointer
videos.description: Adam Flagler drills the 3-point shot at the buzzer as Baylor takes the lead into halftime against Iowa State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Adam Flagler beats the halftime buzzer with logo 3-pointer) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gabe Kalscheur knocks down the 2nd-chance triple
videos.description: Gabe Kalscheur takes advantage of the second chance opportunity and knocks down the triple for Iowa State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Gabe Kalscheur knocks down the 2nd-chance triple) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Bridges splashes a quick transition 3
videos.description: Jalen Bridges catches and shoots the smooth trey giving Baylor a 7-point advantage.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Bridges splashes a quick transition 3) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Bridges catches fire from the 3-point line
videos.description: Jalen Bridges scores another triple and hypes up the crowd as Baylor goes up by 8.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jalen Bridges catches fire from the 3-point line) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dale Bonner steals the rock and takes it in for the and-1
videos.description: Dale Bonner comes up with a steal for Baylor and goes coast-to-coast for the and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dale Bonner steals the rock and takes it in for the and-1) 2023/03/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hason Ward denies Flo Thamba's dunk attempt
videos.description: Hason Ward flies in for a big-time rejection against the Baylor Bears.

videos.headline: Hammer guy called in to fix protruding nail during Iowa State-Baylor
